high_descs: Turn around and walk to the stove, look up at the cupboard to the right of the microwave.
Open the cupboard, take a mug out, close the door.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Put the mug in the fridge to the right of the lettuce, close the door, take the mug out of the fridge, close the door.
Turn right and walk to the shelf across the room.
Put the mug down on the shelf to the left of the bowl.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk to the right side of the stove where it meets the counter.
Look up and open the cupboard on the right and pick up the mug that's up there then close the cupboard.
Turn around and take a step to your left then walk forward to the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the shelves at the far end of the room on the wall.
Put the mug under the sponge to the left of the clear bowl on the second shelf from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the shelf.

Open the fridge put in and out the mug then close the fridge
